# Language Configuration

**Agent chat language**: CHAT_LANGUAGE_PLACEHOLDER
**Project language**: PROJECT_LANGUAGE_PLACEHOLDER

## Language Settings

- **Agent chat language**: Language for communication with Kiro AI agent
- **Project language**: Language for project-specific documentation, GitHub Issues, and Pull Requests

## Notes

- Global configuration (~/.kiro/) is always in English
- Project-specific files (.kiro/ in each project) can use the configured project language
- This includes: project documentation, Issue descriptions, PR descriptions, commit messages

